description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Core Strength ' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Strengthen your core with Pete during 5-minutes of bodyweight exercises. ...
